data.title: Converse Rubber Tracks Sample Library
data.description: The Converse Rubber Tracks Sample Library is a growing collection of audio samples recorded at Converse Rubber Tracks studios. The library is free to use and all samples are completely royalty free – no strings attached. We partnered with Indaba Music to create the site that features over 10,000 high quality one shots, loops, and stems.
